5. Example Pipeline

Question

Why did a civilization fragment?

Step 1

Evidence Mesh ingests:
	•	drought proxies
	•	settlement shrinkage
	•	burial changes
	•	trade interruptions
	•	genome shifts

Step 2

Population Flow Engine checks:
	•	did people disperse?
	•	mix with neighbors?
	•	vanish locally but continue elsewhere?

Step 3

Seed Forge creates:
	•	elites under scarcity
	•	farmers under stress
	•	traders under route collapse
	•	migrants under pressure

Step 4

Arena runs scenarios:
	•	hoarding
	•	rebellion
	•	adaptation
	•	religious stabilization
	•	relocation

Step 5

Invariant Extractor returns:
	•	fragmentation robust under drought + trade stress
	•	invasion-only model weak
	•	ritual-centralization delays collapse but cannot prevent it

Step 6

Render Layer shows:
	•	animated migration
	•	shrinking city cores
	•	branching family lines
	•	conflict heat map
	•	confidence overlay

That is GI:HRE in motion.

